These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
7 different pets are kept: frog, pony, goat, mouse, snake, guinea-pig, cat
7 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, whist, poker, billiard, chess, backgammon
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the snake is the dutch##1
 3. the person playing billiard is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person playing poker is between the person playing backgammon and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person playing whist##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the frog is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing canasta##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person playing whist##1
15. the person playing chess is on the left of the german##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Pet         | goat | snake | frog | pony | cat  | guinea-pig  | mouse    |
| Game     | billiard  | chess         | canasta     | mah-jongg    | whist | poker     | backgammon     |

