 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the owner of the frog##1
 8. the fan of rock is the farmhouse house##1
 9. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the fan of disco is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person eating strawberry and the fan of reggae##2
14. the owner of the frog is on the left of the cottage house##1
15. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
16. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the cottage house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
